high_descs: Move forward to the counter on the left side of the stove
Pick up the knife on the counter
Turn left head move forward turn right on the counter beside the toaster
Put the knife on the plate beside the toaster
Pick up the plate with knife on the counter
Turn right then head to the sink on your left
Put the plate with knife in the sink
anns.task_desc: Put the plate with knife in the sink

high_descs: Face the counter on the left of the stove in front of you.
Pick up the knife from the counter in front of you.
Turn around and face the toaster to your left.
Place the knife on the plate to the left of the toaster in front of you.
Take the plate with the knife from the counter in front of you.
Turn right then face the sink to your left.
Place the plate with the knife inside the sink in front of you.
anns.task_desc: Place a bowl with a knife in the sink.

high_descs: Move a step forward to the stove.
Pick up the knife from the counter, left of the stove.
Take the knife and turn around, then face the counter on the right.
Place the knife in the plate on the left side of the counter.
Pick up the plate from the left side of the counter.
Carry the plate and take a few steps to the right to find the sink.
Place the plate and knife in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Move a plate and knife to the sink.
